headline: Global Payments Appoints Nathan Rozof as Head of Investor Relations
summary: ATLANTA, September 30, 2025--Global Payments Inc. (NYSE: GPN) today announced the appointment of Nathan Rozof, CFA, as head of Investor Relations.
